raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"shopping_mall\")
Mabel: Good Afternoon sleepyhead!
Player: Hey! Was totally not sleeping.
Mabel: Yeah right 😆
Player: What are you up to?
Mabel: Shopping!
Mabel: Nina came by and uhm...
Mabel: Well... she lectured me on my wardrobe...
Mabel: She said I dress like a senior teacher 🥹
Player: Wow
Mabel: Do you think that's true babe?
- I don't!
	Player: I don't!
	Player: I think the way you dress is great ❤️
	Mabel: Thanks for the reassurance hehe
	Mabel: But Nina insisted that we update my closets
- It wouldn't hurt to fit in a little bit! [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: It wouldn't hurt to fit in a little bit!
	Mabel: She said the exact same thing to me 😳
Mabel: img: mabel/22
Mabel: Surprise!
Player: Hey pretty girl!
Mabel: That's me hehe
if Story.mabel_trust >= 50:
	Mabel: Oh and here's Nina too
	Mabel: img: nina/2
	- Like day and night!
		Player: Like day and night!
		Mabel: 😆
	- Could you send me her Social btw? [#blackheart]
		set Story.black_heart += 1
		Player: Could you send me her Social?
		Mabel: Oh sure! 
		Mabel: I have it but it's a paid social 😅
		Player: Oh interesting
		Mabel: You should get it now
		set PhoneUnlocks.reveal = \"nina\"
		Player: Thanks!
Mabel: We're about to go shopping, just us girls hehe
Mabel: But I'll show you what I try on! 😘
Player: Can't wait
do advance_time(2, 30)
Mabel: Okay!
Mabel: So Nina wants me to wear one of these for tonight
Mabel: So help me pick one pls
Player: Sounds good
Mabel: Are you ready?? 😋
Player: Born ready
Mabel: Okay uhm...
Mabel: Exhibit A
Mabel: img: mabel/23
Player: Whoa, nice!
Player: Simple, cute and charming
Mabel: Aaaand exhibit B! 🙈
Mabel: img: mabel/24
Player: Wow
Mabel: I DIDN'T PICK THIS ONE!
Mabel: Nina insisted I try it
Mabel: And she took the picture pretty low didn't she 😅
Mabel: Well what do you think? 😊
- I like the first one! [#love]
	set Story.flag = \"ClubOutfitA\"
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 2
	Player: I like the first one!
	Mabel: I like it too
	Mabel: I've never worn these kind of shorts before
	Mabel: But Nina said it would be a shame to not show off my bum 🥹
	Mabel: That was seriously the last thing on my mind and now I'm a bit self conscious about it
- The second one! [#lust]
	set Story.flag = \"ClubOutfitB\"
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: The second one!
	Mabel: Seriously??
	Mabel: Nina's been smirking at me ever since I tried it on 😭
	Mabel: My legs feel super exposed
	Mabel: Thought: My panties show when I'm sitting too
	Player: You look seriously good!
	Mabel: Wow, if my boyfriend says so then..
	Mabel: I guess I could do this for you
- Which one do you like? [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	set Story.flag = \"ClubOutfitA\"
	Player: Which one do you like?
	Mabel: I like the first one more 😇
	Player: Then go with that one!
	Player: It was tough, you make every outfit work!
	Mabel: Omg shush, don't make me blush out here in front of Nina
- Nina probably knows better than me [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 2
	set Story.flag = \"ClubOutfitB\"
	Player: Nina probably knows better than me
	Mabel: I guess so
	Mabel: But I was thinking maybe..
	Mabel: Thought: Maybe you could tell me which one would look nice on me
	Mabel: Nevermind actually 😊
	Player: 😊
Mabel: Okay, we're going back to my place and then heading there after
Mabel: I'm super nervous lol
Mabel: Wish me luck 😅
Player: Good luck!
do advance_time(4, 48)
do Story.set_location(\"nightclub\")
Mabel: I decided I hate these types of clubs 😑
Player: Already? 😂
Player: What's going on??
Mabel: OMG
Mabel: It's totally dark and smells a bit weird
Mabel: But somehow lights keep shining in my face
Mabel: Music is blasting in my ears
Mabel: And strangers keep bumping into me
Player: Ah I hate when that happens
Player: People stepping on my feet
Mabel: OMG Exactly
Mabel: I feel like I had to watch myself the whole time
Mabel: Nina is sooo into it though
Mabel: She's already dancing with everyone
Mabel: Thought: Mostly... guys though
Mabel: I'm just standing in the corner watching her
if Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitA\"):
	Mabel: img: mabel/25
elif Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitB\"):
	Mabel: img: mabel/26
Mabel: Hi 😊
Player: Hey! 😍
Mabel: She asked me to take pics of her though lol
- You're not having a blast I take it
	Player: You're not having a blast I take it
	Mabel: 😅
	Mabel: Is it bad that I'm not?
	Player: Not at all!
	Player: At least it's no longer a mystery
	Mabel: Well idk
	Mabel: I feel like even though I'm here
	Mabel: I'm not really here
	Mabel: Am I making sense?
	Mabel: Everyone looks like they're having so much fun!
	Mabel: But there's a frequency that I'm just not on
	Player: I see what you mean
	Mabel: Yeah, I wonder if that's something that you can learn
	Player: Only one way to find out 😂
	Mabel: Do I wanna? 😂
- What's Nina up to?
	Player: What's she up to?
	Mabel: You want to see Nina? Why?
	- I'm just a little curious [#distrust]
		set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
		Mabel: Uhm... 
		Mabel: Thought: I want you to look at me, not her
		Mabel: I guess I could..
		Mabel: img: nina/3
		- Wow [#blackheart]
			set Story.black_heart += 1
			set Story.mabel_desire += 1
			Player: Wow
			Mabel: Babe?? What you mean wow??? 😅 
			Mabel: Are you feeling okay, silly head?
			Mabel: Thought: Is this really what you like!?
		- Oh uhh I didn't think that's what I'd see
			Player: Oh uhh I didn't think that's what I'd see
			Mabel: Yeah, I was hoping you'd change your mind 😭
			Mabel: I don't know what kind of dance that is
	- Or you can just tell me what's going on [#lust]
		set Story.mabel_desire += 1
		Player: Or you can just tell me what's going on
		Mabel: I don't even know how to describe what I'm seeing to be honest 🥹
		Mabel: She's like dancing with her butt all over... a guy
		Mabel: Omg this is like too much 😭
		Player: You can say that again 😆
if Story.mabel_trust <= 50:
	Mabel: Hold on one second, Nina's calling me
	Mabel: Let me see what she wants
	Player: Tyt
	Mabel: Thought: Is he staring at me!?
	Mabel: Thought: Oh no we made eye contact again...
	do heart(2)
	if Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitA\"):
		do echo_set([\"27\"])
	elif Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitB\"):
		do echo_set([\"28\"])
	Mabel: Give me a sec babe
	Player: Sure thing
	Mabel: sfx: none: I'm sorry I...
	Mabel: sfx: none: I'm here with my friend
	Mabel: sfx: none: I don't drink, thank you though
	Mabel: sfx: none: Where?
	Mabel: Thought: Why would he ask me to go to his room
	Mabel: Thought: Do people just go straight to each other's room after a chat?
	Mabel: sfx: none: No I.. I have a boyfriend I mean
	Mabel: sfx: none: I'm sorry, I kinda don't want to
	Player: You still there?
	Mabel: Hold on one sec
	Player: Okay
	do echo_clear()
	do heart(0)
else:
	Mabel: I wish you were here baaabe
	Player: We'll see each other soon!
	Mabel: I knooow but
	Mabel: I kinda want you to... uhm...
	Mabel: See me in this outfit 🥰
	Mabel: Even though it's totally embarassing
	Mabel: Like in person
	Player: That would be nice!
	Mabel: Well since you aren't here
	Mabel: I can pose for you
	Mabel: I'll ask Nina to take a picture to pay me back lol
	Mabel: What kind of pose do you want to see? Hehe
	- Something cute 😊
		Player: Something cute 😊
		Mabel: Coming riiiight up!
		if Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitA\"):
			Mabel: img: mabel/29
		elif Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitB\"):
			Mabel: img: mabel/30
		Mabel: How's that?
		Player: SUPER CUTE 😍
		Mabel: Hehe, I knew you'd like it 😌❤️
		Player: I love it
		Mabel: 🥰
	- Something sexy 👀 [#lust]
		set Story.mabel_desire += 1
		Player: Something sexy 👀
		Mabel: W-what? 🫣
		Mabel: Seriously?
		Mabel: I mean.. I guess it isn't so weird
		Mabel: Thought: Girls do this kind of thing with their boyfriends right?
		Mabel: Thought: I mean yeah... just looking around at the others
		Player: Still there?
		Mabel: Sorry! I was aah!
		Player: You were aah?
		Mabel: Very aah
		Mabel: Okay uhm... I'll try
		Mabel: But don't show this to anyone or I'll cry okay? 🥹
		if Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitA\"):
			Mabel: img: mabel/31
		elif Story.has_flag(\"ClubOutfitB\"):
			Mabel: img: mabel/32
		Mabel: Does that do it? 😖
		Mabel: Tell me if it's bad so I retake it
		Player: It's perfect 😍
		Mabel: Phew 🙃
		Mabel: Glad to hear that lol
		Mabel: Seriously I'm a fish out of water 😂
Mabel: I think I'll go home now
Mabel: It's too much to take in on one night 😭
Mabel: And it's really dark outside so I'll have to skedaddle
Mabel: If I don't answer in 15 minutes, it means I've been kidnapped!! 😭😭😭
Player: You'll be fine 😂❤️
Mabel: Okay fiiine
Mabel: Going now
Player: Be safe!
Mabel: Thanks, mwah! 😘
do advance_time(0, 15)
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Okay safe at home now
Mabel: Changed and cozied up
Mabel: Jeez that was... an experience
Mabel: My ears are still ringing from all the loud music
Player: Did you have fun?
Mabel: Uhm... I wouldn't say I had fun but it was nice to spend time with Nina
Mabel: Thought: All that attention though was something I never felt before
Mabel: Have you been to one?
Player: Not many, just a few
Player: I went to other night when you were busy
Mabel: Oh
Mabel: With who??
Player: That friend I made in orientation!
Mabel: Thought: Did I make him feel lonely?
Mabel: Sorry babe.. 😞
Player: Sorry for what? Don't worry 😅
Mabel: I'm just a worry wart
Mabel: What did you do out anyway?
Mabel: You didn't drink and go crazy like those people I saw today 🙃
- I didn't! [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: I didn't!
	Mabel: You suuure?
	Mabel: You're not hiding anything from me are you? 😙
	Mabel: You can tell me anything 🥰
	Player: Seriously haha
	Mabel: I'm just teasing you silly
	Mabel: I know you're responsible 
	Mabel: I can always lean on you for anything 🥰
	Player: Of course!
- I would have if you were with me [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I would have if you were with me
	Mabel: Oh my god, shush 😂🥰
	Mabel: You're so silly
	Mabel: But maybe I wouldn't mind it
	Mabel: I'd feel totally safe with you hehe
	Mabel: Thought: Nobody could try to steal me away
	Player: 😉
- Maybe just a little [#distrust]
	set Story.mabel_trust -= 1
	Player: Maybe just a little
	Mabel: Baabe!
	Mabel: You shouldn't do that silly 😶
	Player: It seriously was just a little
	Mabel: Well if you say so
	Mabel: I just don't want to lose my boyfriend to that kind of thing 🥺
